\pard{\pntext\f6\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf6\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1 What is Game?\par
\pard An activity with rules. It is a form of play often\par
but not always involving conflict, either with other players, with the game system itself, or\par
with randomness/fate/luck. Most games have goals, but not all (for example, \i\f1 The Sims \i0\f0 and\par
\i\f1 SimCity\i0\f0 ). Most games have defined start and end points, but not all (for example, \i\f1 World of\par
Warcraft \i0\f0 and \i\f1 Dungeons & Dragons\i0\f0 ). Most games involve decision making on the part of the\par
players, but not all (for example, \i\f1 Candy Land \i0\f0 and \i\f1 Chutes and Ladders\i0\f0 ). A video game is a\par
\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1 game (as defined above) that uses a digital video screen of some kind, in some way\par
