\pard{\pntext\f6\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf6\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\ulnone\b\f3\fs20 Feature List\b0\f0\par
\pard\tab A list that details key features or selling points of the game. In published games, \par
