\par
\ul\b\f2\fs22 G\fs17 OALS\ulnone\f3\fs20\par
\b0\f0 Layered on top of all things are game goals. The ultimate game goal is, of course, the victory\par
condition. Sometimes, goals in games are called \ldblquote missions\rdblquote  or \ldblquote quests.\rdblquote\par
Goals typically provide rewards that motivate players to defeat creatures, search for treasure,\par
equip themselves with better and better armor, and compete against their friends.\par
